Selecting all the following code and then trying to comment it out does nothing.  This only affects languages that specify a comment with a start and end component (eg CSS, HTML).  I would expect it to comment out the following css code:

``` css
/* General Overrides */

.codelab code.prettyprint {
  color: white; /* default color in case offline */
}
```

ref https://github.com/atom/language-css/issues/39
